      • deletePerson

        @DeleteMapping("/deletePerson/{ssn}")
public ResponseObject deletePerson​(@PathVariable
                                   long ssn)
        Attempts to delete a Person entry in the database given ssn parameter.
        Parameters:
        ssn - - social security number
        Returns:
        a string ' "Deleted: ssn | lastname | firstname | getAge | getGender | getCity | getCountry " ' if an entity with given SSN exists.
        Otherwise an error message indicating that such entity does not exist:
        Error: Entity with SSN '...' doesn't exist.
